00:52:07,332 --> 00:52:08,701
Lihatlah Anda.

677
00:52:09,272 --> 00:52:10,372
Ini ulah Anda sendiri.

678
00:52:11,272 --> 00:52:13,102
Anda pantas menerima
semua ini.

679
00:52:13,441 --> 00:52:15,512
Makanya kenapa
Anda sangat kejam?

680
00:52:16,741 --> 00:52:18,381
